name: Manga
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Manga Token is a reward, payment and staking token for the manga industry to facilitate supporting your favourite manga artists through a new form of digital merchandise called Manga NFTs and we are building the world largest Manga NFT marketplace for authentic manga collectibles from original manga artists.
